__________________________________________|_______________________________________________________________________________
 Audio Panel Configuration                |   Ensure correct audio panel selections are made on flight deck to monitor VHF audio.
__________________________________________|_______________________________________________________________________________
 BITE Test Interpretation                 |   Familiarity with BITE codes and messages specific to the installed VHF Transceiver model is necessary. (Ref: Vendor CMM XX-XX-XX).
__________________________________________|_______________________________________________________________________________
 Recording Discrepancies                  |   Any failures or deviations from expected results during the test must be accurately recorded and reported.
